des:
Chill Beats presents the ultimate chill tracks to help you study, concentrate, or just relax.

Just open the skill, and let the lo-fi music envelop you in a relaxing cloud of loving chillness.

Simple. Easy. Relaxing. 

The very definition of chill.

Just say next for a new track or previous for the last one.
